Package: GenesRanking
Title: A Package for Identifying Biomarkers in scRNA-Seq Data
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Petros", "Paplomatas", email = "p.paplomatas@hotmail.com",
         role = c("cre","aut"),
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2691-2767")),
  person("Aristidis", "Vrahatis", email = "avrahatis@math.uoa.gr", role = "aut"))
Description: GenesRanking is an R package designed for efficient biomarker identification from scRNA-seq data.
  Offering a user-friendly interface, it enables users to employ 20 distinct
  dimensionality reduction techniques, including various filter and machine learning-based 
  feature selection methods. Its purpose is to simplify and streamline the biomarker
  identification process, providing essential tools for biological data analysis.
